SUMMARY:Asana Day: The Art of the Possible (Session 1)
DTSTAMP:20260622T103707Z
DTSTART:20260805T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:For the first time ever\, the Asana team is coming to Rice for 
	an immersive\, three-session series designed to transform how Rice moves. 
	We're pulling back the curtain on why Rice is investing in Asana and\, mor
	e importantly\, how your colleagues are already using it to turn messy wor
	kflows into organized masterpieces. Join us for this productivity power-up
	 and snag some exclusive Asana swag! This is an event you don't want to mi
	ss. Seats are limited.\n\nhttps://events.rice.edu/ofs/event/431057-asana-d
	ay-the-art-of-the-possible-session-1\n\nFrom Rice University - Open to the
